						<p><div class="item">
<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/en/Dossiers/S-T-Issues/Biotechnology/Related-developments/Ethiopia-committee-on-biotechnology-formed" title="Ethiopia committee on biotechnology formed" alt="link">Ethiopia committee on biotechnology formed</a></h2>

	
					<p>A Public-Private Partnership Committee on Biotechnology (PPPCB) was formed in Ethiopia to advocate for the amendment of the biosafety law, and also to negotiate cotton biotechnology access from international genetically modified (GM) cotton technology providers. This was agreed upon during the biotechnology stakeholders meeting held in Addis Ababa, Ethiopia, on April 14, 2010. (Source ISAAA, 27 April 2010)</p>
							<p><span class="date">21/05/2010</span></p>
	<div class="cnt">
