						<p><div class="item">
<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/en/Dossiers/S-T-Issues/Biotechnology/Related-developments/Biosafety-Bibliographic-Database-Bibliosafety" title="Biosafety Bibliographic Database (Bibliosafety)" alt="link">Biosafety Bibliographic Database (Bibliosafety)</a></h2>

	
					<p>








 




  
  

	
	<a href="/var/knowledge/storage/images/media/images/icgeb/299072-1-eng-GB/ICGEB.jpg" rel="lightbox[]" >	
	  </a>
	
		
			
	
  	






	 
  





	The ICGEB Biosafety Unit launched a newly restructured <a href="http://bibliosafety.icgeb.org/" target="_blank">Biosafety Bibliographic Database (Bibliosafety)</a>. Key improvements revolve around a more powerful simple search using a similar approach to Google. Other improvements include the listing of search output by the degree of relevancy rather than by publication year, a clearer layout of each record and direct links, where available, to DOI, corresponding author email and journal website.</p>
							<p><span class="date">26/04/2010</span></p>
	<div class="cnt">
	<a class="link" href="/en/Dossiers/S-T-Issues/Biotechnology/Related-developments/Biosafety-Bibliographic-Database-Bibliosafety">Read more...</a>
</div>
<br class="cl">
</div>
