						<p><div class="item">
<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/en/Dossiers/S-T-Issues/Biotechnology/Related-developments/Biosafety-South-Africa-to-be-launched" title="Biosafety South Africa to be launched" alt="link">Biosafety South Africa to be launched</a></h2>

	
					<p>South Africa's Department of Science and Technology (DST) through the PlantBio Trust, will launch Biosafety South Africa to support biotechnology innovation by ensuring the development of safe and sustainable biotechnological products. &quot;The field of biological diversity, which is essentially the focus of biosafety, is a wide and complex one and touches on issues as diverse as international law, trans-boundary agreements, the Antarctic Treaty System, hazardous wastes, international justice, persistent organic pollutants and atomic energy, to name a few Deputy Minister of Science and Technology Derek Hanekom said. (Source: Web Newswire, 28 March 2010)</p>
