<h2><a class="listing" style="link" href="/en/Dossiers/S-T-Issues/Biotechnology/Related-developments/Uganda-Scientists-told-to-simplify-data" title="Uganda: Scientists told to simplify data" alt="link">Uganda: Scientists told to simplify data</a></h2>

	
					<p>Scientists have been asked to simplify the information on biotechnology for people to understand better. &quot;Scientists' attitudes and mindsets must change. They need to target appropriate audiences with the information they need,&quot; said Dan Kiambi, a senior official from the Kenyan chapter of the Open Forum for Agricultural Biotechnology. (Source: All Africa, 17 March 2010)</p>
